Module com.psymk6
Package com.psymk6.models

Class SnakeModel

java.lang.Object
com.psymk6.abstracts.CanvasObjectModel
com.psymk6.abstracts.LiveCanvasObjectModel
com.psymk6.models.SnakeModel
public class SnakeModel extends LiveCanvasObjectModel
The SnakeModel class represents the model for the snake object in the game. It extends the LiveCanvasObjectModel and provides properties such as speed, length, direction, and body points.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Mateusz Klocek
